atan Arnautovi\u0107]] ||9||4\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Borislav Cvetkovi\u0107]]{{efn|name=YPA}} ||9||1 \n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[\u017deljko Hohnjec]] ||9||1\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Marin Kurtela]] ||6||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Drago Dumbovi\u0107]] ||6||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Milan \u0106alasan]] ||4||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Zvonko Mari\u0107]] ||3||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Branko Dev\u010di\u0107]] ||3||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Mladen Munjakovi\u0107]] ||3||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Radimir Bobinac]] ||2||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[Davor Braun]] ||2||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Yugoslavia}} [[\u010cedomir Jovi\u010devi\u0107]] ||1||0\n|-\n|{{flagicon|Australia}} [[Edi Krncevic|Edward Krn\u010devi\u0107]] ||1||0\n|- class=\"sortbottom\"\n| colspan=3 | '''Coach''': [[Miroslav Bla\u017eevi\u0107]]\n|}\n{{notelist}}\n*League topscorer: [[Snje\u017ean Cerin|Snje\u0161ko Cerin]] ([[Dinamo Zagreb]]) - 19\n\n==Results==\n{{#invoke:Sports results|main\n|matches_style=FBR|solid_cell=grey\n|team1=BUD|team2=DIN|team3=HAJ|team4=OFK|team5=OLI\n|team6=OSI|team7=PAR|team8=RNI|team9=RSB|team10=RIJ\n|team11=SAR|team12=SLO|team13=TET|team14=VAR|team15=VEL\n|team16=VOJ|team17=ZAG|team18=\u017dEL\n\n|name_BUD=[[FK Budu\u0107nost Podgorica|Budu\u0107nost]]\n|match_BUD_DIN=1\u20130\n|match_BUD_HAJ=0\u20130\n|match_BUD_OFK=4\u20132\n|match_BUD_OLI=4\u20132\n|match_BUD_OSI=3\u20132\n|match_BUD_PAR=1\u20133\n|match_BUD_RNI=2\u20130\n|match_BUD_RSB=1\u20131\n|match_BUD_RIJ=2\u20132\n|match_BUD_SAR=1\u20130\n|match_BUD_SLO=2\u20130\n|match_BUD_TET=4\u20132\n|match_BUD_VAR=2\u20130\n|match_BUD_VEL=2\u20130\n|match_BUD_VOJ=3\u20131\n|match_BUD_ZAG=4\u20130\n|match_BUD_\u017dEL=0\u20131\n\n|name_DIN=[[GNK Dinamo Zagreb|Dinamo Zagreb]]\n|match_DIN_BUD=1\u20130\n|match_DIN_HAJ=[[Eternal derby (Croatia)|0\u20130]]\n|match_DIN_OFK=0\u20130\n|match_DIN_OLI=2\u20132\n|match_DIN_OSI=1\u20130\n|match_DIN_PAR=1\u20130\n|match_D