n|match_ZAG_OFK=1\u20131\n|match_ZAG_OLI=1\u20130\n|match_ZAG_OSI=2\u20131\n|match_ZAG_PAR=0\u20131\n|match_ZAG_RNI=0\u20132\n|match_ZAG_RSB=0\u20133\n|match_ZAG_RIJ=1\u20131\n|match_ZAG_SAR=0\u20131\n|match_ZAG_SLO=2\u20130\n|match_ZAG_TET=2\u20131\n|match_ZAG_VAR=3\u20132\n|match_ZAG_VEL=2\u20130\n|match_ZAG_VOJ=2\u20130\n|match_ZAG_\u017dEL=1\u20132\n\n|name_\u017dEL=[[FK \u017deljezni\u010dar Sarajevo|\u017deljezni\u010dar]]\n|match_\u017dEL_BUD=3\u20131\n|match_\u017dEL_DIN=3\u20131\n|match_\u017dEL_HAJ=1\u20132\n|match_\u017dEL_OFK=2\u20130\n|match_\u017dEL_OLI=1\u20131\n|match_\u017dEL_OSI=1\u20130\n|match_\u017dEL_PAR=0\u20131\n|match_\u017dEL_RNI=4\u20130\n|match_\u017dEL_RSB=0\u20130\n|match_\u017dEL_RIJ=1\u20132\n|match_\u017dEL_SAR=[[Sarajevo derby|4\u20131]]\n|match_\u017dEL_SLO=1\u20131\n|match_\u017dEL_TET=6\u20130\n|match_\u017dEL_VAR=4\u20132\n|match_\u017dEL_VEL=2\u20130\n|match_\u017dEL_VOJ=2\u20131\n|match_\u017dEL_ZAG=2\u20130\n\n|update= \n|source=\n}}\n\n==Season statistics==\n*Widest winning margin: '''7 goals''':\n**Dinamo Zagreb 7\u20130 NK Zagreb (13 September 1981)\n**Hajduk Split 7\u20130 Teteks (31 March 1982)\n*Most goals in a match: '''9 goals''':\n**Rijeka 5\u20134 Radni\u010dki Ni\u0161 (23 August 1981)\n**Partizan 7\u20132 Sloboda (25 April 1982)\n\n==See also==\n*[[1981\u201382 Yugoslav Second League]]\n*[[1981\u201382 Yugoslav Cup]]\n*[[1981\u201382 NK Dinamo Zagreb season]]\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesj/joeghist.html Yugoslavia Domestic Football Full Tables]\n\n{{Yugoslav First League}}\n{{1981\u201382 in European Football (UEFA)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1981-82 Yugoslav First League}}\n[[Category:Yugoslav First League seasons]]\n[[Category:1981\u201382 in European association football leagues|Yugo]]\n[[Category:1981\u201382 in Yugoslavian football]]\n", "name_user": "Jolicnikola", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eLeague table", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1981%E2%80%9382_Yugoslav_First_League"