eidelh\u00e4user), \u0160estidom\u00ed (S\u00e4chsst\u00e4dten) and [[Zadn\u00ed Rennerovky]] (Hinter Rennerbauden).\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e9}}\n* [http://www.oustrazne.cz/ Municipal website]\n\n{{Trutnov District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Strazne}}\n[[Category:Villages in Trutnov District]]\n[[Category:Stamp mills]]\n[[Category:Mines in the Czech Republic]]\n\n\n{{HradecKr\u00e1lov\u00e9-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name                    = Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e9\n| native_name             = \n| other_name              = \n| settlement_type         = Village\n<!-- images, nickname, motto -->\n| image_skyline           = Strazne 01.JPG\n| image_caption           = Center of the village\n| image_flag              = Flag_of_Strazne.svg\n| image_shield            = Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e9 CoA.jpg\n| motto                   = \n| nickname                = \n| etymology               = \n<!-- location -->\n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = Czech Republic\n| subdivision_type1       = \n| subdivision_name1       = \n| subdivision_type2       = [[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Hradec Kr\u00e1lov\u00e9 Region|Hradec Kr\u00e1lov\u00e9]]\n| subdivision_type3       = [[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n| subdivision_name3       = [[Trutnov District|Trutnov]]\n| subdivision_type4       = Little District\n| subdivision_name4       = Vrchlab\u00ed\n<!-- maps and coordinates -->\n| image_map               = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = Czechia\n| pushpin_relief          = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = Location in the Czech Republic \n| coordinates             = {{coord|50|40|55|N|15|38|43|E|display=inline,title}}\n| coordinates_footnotes   = \n<!-- government type, leaders -->\n| leader_title            = Mayor\n| leader_name             = Ji\u0159\u00ed Zl\u00