 are [[Friesovy Boudy]] (Friesbauden), [[Herl\u00edkovice]] (Hackelsdorf), [[H\u0159\u00edb\u011bc\u00ed Boudy]] (F\u00fcllebauden), [[Hus\u00ed Boudy]] (Gansbauden), [[Jezern\u00ed Domky]] (Teichh\u00e4user), [[Kr\u00e1sn\u00e1 Pl\u00e1\u0148]] (Sch\u00f6ne Lahn), [[Lahrovy Boudy]] (Lahrbauden), Ml\u00fdnsk\u00e9 Domky (M\u00fchlberg) Well V\u00fdhl\u00e9dach (H\u00f6henschmiede), [[P\u0159edn\u00ed Rennerovky]] (Vorder Rennerbauden), Seidlovy Domky (Seidelh\u00e4user), \u0160estidom\u00ed (S\u00e4chsst\u00e4dten) and [[Zadn\u00ed Rennerovky]] (Hinter Rennerbauden).\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e9}}\n* [http://www.oustrazne.cz/ Municipal website]\n\n{{Trutnov District}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Strazne}}\n[[Category:Villages in Trutnov District]]\n[[Category:Stamp mills]]\n[[Category:Mines in the Czech Republic]]\n\n\n{{HradecKr\u00e1lov\u00e9-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Str%C3%A1%C5%BEn%C3%A9"}
{"title_page": "Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=\n|image_shield = Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1.svg\n|image_flag = Flag_of_Strazna_CZ.svg\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[Pardubice Region|Pardubice]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District|\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|54|27|N|16|42|44|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2=10.64\n|population_total=111|population_as_of=2006\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=605\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=561&nbsp;32\n}}\n\n'''Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1''' is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District]] in the [[Pardubice Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|10.64|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 111 (as at 3&nbsp;July 2006).\n\nStr\u00e1\u017en\u00e1 lies approximately {{convert|24|km|mi|0}} east of [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed]], {{convert|69|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Pardubice]], and {{convert|166|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n{{commons category|Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1}}\n*[http://www.pardubice.czso.cz/xe/redakce.nsf/i/ciselnik_obci_v_kraji/$File/ciselnik_obci.xls Regional Statistical Office: Municipalities of Pardubice Region]\n\n{{\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Strazna}}\n[[Category:Villages in \u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District]]\n\n\n{{Pardubice-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=\n|image_shield = Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1.svg\n|image_flag = Flag_of_Strazna_CZ.svg\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[Pardubice Region|Pardubice]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District|\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|54|27|N|16|42|44|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2=10.64\n|population_total=111|population_as_of=2006\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=605\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=561&nbsp;32\n}}\n\n'''Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1''' is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District]] in the [[Pardubice Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|10.64|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 111 (as at 3&nbsp;July 2006).\n\nStr\u00e1\u017en\u00e1 lies approximately {{convert|24|km|mi|0}} east of [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed]], {{convert|69|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Pardubice]], and {{convert|166|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n{{commons category|Str\u00e1\u017en\u00e1}}\n*[http://www.pardubice.czso.cz/xe/redakce.nsf/i/ciselnik_obci_v_kraji/$File/ciselnik_obci.xls Regional Statistical Office: Municipalities of Pardubice Region]\n\n{{\u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Strazna}}\n[[Category:Villages in \u00dast\u00ed nad Orlic\u00ed District]]\n\n\n{{Pardubice-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Str%C3%A1%C5%BEn%C3%A1"}
